{"tid":613843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"阿叔擘髀坐巴士　同座男不滿身體接觸互毆","createTime":"2018-04-02T04:45:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T10:28:59.000Z","uid":147194,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f1f79d5b54c0f99996d71ab95d6509b85e043a6b","tid":613843,"uid":147194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T04:45:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180402/photo/bkn-20180402035938152-0402_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180402123417\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180402%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180402035938152-0402_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180402123417&h=c013cf26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n荃灣發生打架傷人案，昨(1日)深夜11時許，一輛路線269M來往天水圍天恩邨至葵涌祖堯邨的九巴，沿屯門公路往荃灣方向行駛，至汀九段錦柏豪苑對開，2男子同坐在下層近落車門旁邊的雙人座，其中姓鍾<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（62歲）</span></span>男子，被指<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">擘開大髀而坐</span></span>，並觸碰到身旁姓楊（30歲）男子，雙方展開罵戰，繼而在車廂互毆，姓葉（27歲）車長見狀，遂將車停在一旁及報警。<br />\n<br />\n警員到場調查，鍾頭部受傷流血，而楊眼角受傷，分別送院治理。警方調查後，兩人同涉嫌在公眾地方打架被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n東網<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180402/bkn-20180402035938152-0402_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180402%2Fbkn-20180402035938152-0402_00822_001.html&d=Ps3i2e1DJ1NlaMvjxML7hpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=b8b30aad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180402/bkn-20180402035938152-0402_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0632d7523c6a915718cb5df434c60da5f31614cb","tid":613843,"uid":147194,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T04:46:12.000Z","msg":"兩蚊坐巴士重要當正自己屋企噉樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfdcf9be6b725a097fae31da70a0b61ef39c0208","tid":613843,"uid":176166,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T04:47:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d5ecc023566a88bf5adbf1ccc883a94d6c30e94","tid":613843,"uid":134683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T04:50:00.000Z","msg":"呢d坐車黐黐貢阿叔真係攞去填海啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c537bd19d8cd42a79f89b7fba27102c12072d93","tid":613843,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T04:51:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81df05e24b9ec97663f5fb185cdc3d06cd7645fd","tid":613843,"uid":66221,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"6c537bd19d8cd42a79f89b7fba27102c12072d93","tid":613843,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T04:51:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T04:55:39.000Z","msg":"你唔俾人地坐咗先至到個廢老坐埋黎？"},{"pid":"0c30f676204d9aebebd30a3870dea460e49e0baa","tid":613843,"uid":163207,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T05:10:33.000Z","msg":"62歲(擘髀)"},{"pid":"b96d0c8efbd152b322fac073b27a2f5ba5a12792","tid":613843,"uid":29982,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T05:12:40.000Z","msg":"抵撚死，死廢老<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：七人車代步唔搭巴士"},{"pid":"8cbefc2317ba9ee95914a0ad3a15f1dae3a92b63","tid":613843,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T05:19:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b59ed31ff147be98a4aacbb7c319aefd86f2b2c","tid":613843,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T07:05:10.000Z","msg":"坐時兩腿張開，姿態懶散者，是屬於豪言壯語型，就是那類「說得多做得少」的人，他們想的和說的事情，經常是誇大的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20070913/large/2913e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20070913%2Flarge%2F2913e6.jpg&h=bcdaed65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d94c23bf2920e976c57b99c9b7df3111ca5106f","tid":613843,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T07:05:55.000Z","msg":"【男士留意】外國立例擘髀犯法　醫生：唔擘易生癬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170611/small/e08_14_a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170611%2Fsmall%2Fe08_14_a.jpg&h=dd9d959a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n12,153<br />\n<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[西班牙首都馬德里剛剛宣佈，禁止巴士及地鐵乘客擘脾，而紐約更於2014年立例，甚至有乘客因此被拘捕，最終罰款50美金。] 西班牙首都馬德里剛剛宣佈，禁止巴士及地鐵乘客擘脾，而紐約更於2014年立例，甚至有乘客因此被拘捕，最終罰款50美金。<br />\n<br />\n無論是擘髀坐，還是鄰座擘髀令你感到很擠逼，相信很多人都有這些經歷。這類擘髀動作，在外國稱為&quot;menspreading&quot;，即主要針對男士乘客。西班牙首都馬德里剛剛宣佈，禁止巴士及地鐵乘客擘髀，侵佔鄰座乘客空間，不過就未有處罰。反觀紐約2014年已立例禁止乘客擘髀，甚至有乘客因此被拘捕，最終罰款50美金。那到底為甚麼擘髀坐的通常是男性？<br />\n<br />\n註冊醫生鄭志文：「其中一個原因是男士下身的股溝間容易較熱，溫度較高，張開腿感覺會較舒服，特別是穿著緊窄的褲時。」若禁止男士張開腿，對男士健康會否造成影響？鄭醫生續說：「其實很小，勉強地說。若男士下體溫度過熱，可能會影響精子數量，長遠地影響生育能力，不過很少發生。反而有些人本身體溫偏高，或行走很久才乘車，若不能張開腿讓下體抖涼，積聚汗液則有機會患上股溝癬。」<br />\n<br />\n既然如此，男土們麻煩你下次擘髀坐，都不要擘得太大吧。"},{"pid":"f7e37cdad69c4cb696b30d09bf9bd0926cf6cfa8","tid":613843,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T07:22:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01ee32e6bd45d8488591101050a46fda67ce9307","tid":613843,"uid":147194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7e37cdad69c4cb696b30d09bf9bd0926cf6cfa8","tid":613843,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T07:22:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T07:42:20.000Z","msg":"係喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人知道點解？有冇人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f102d1326d94823c65e962ea6ee22db705f6cf3","tid":613843,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d94c23bf2920e976c57b99c9b7df3111ca5106f","tid":613843,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T07:0